      • Bomb

        public Bomb​(boolean car,
            boolean frk,
            byte batteries,
            char digit,
            boolean vowel,
            boolean parallel)
        Constructs a bomb with the specified preconditions
        Parameters:
        car - if there is a lit indicator labeled CAR
        frk - if there is a lit indicator labeled FRK
        batteries - the number of batteries on the bomb
        digit - the last digit of the serial number
        vowel - if there is a vowel in the serial number
        parallel - if the bomb has a long pink port (parallel port)
